                    <div class="icon-circle">
                        <span class="icon-text">ATS</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h3>Applicant Tracking System Optimized</h3>
                <p>
                    CVs are structured to pass modern ATS software used by leading employers across Africa,
                    increasing your chances of being shortlisted.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <div class="icon-circle">
