                <div class="about-card">
                    <h3>Built in Ghana, for Africa</h3>
                    <p>
                        Our templates and workflows reflect how recruitment actually works in Ghana and across Africa,
                        not just in Europe or the US.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card">
                    <h3>Continuous Improvement</h3>
